metadata.description: Welcome to LazyToons, a collection of 3000 AI generated NFTs. Each LazyToon is a unique, non-fungible token operating on the ethereum blockchain. All the LazyToons are made of hundreds of mind blowing traits of body, hair,ears, clothes and many other original accessories. Each lazytoon gives its owner the ability to vote and make decisions about the community's treasury fund, you are the ones who decide! You will also have access to clothing launches of our own brand, raffles, events, and much more! Join our journey, join the LazyToons!!
